title: 'Spectre' stars glam up for James Bond world premiere
text: Blogs 'Spectre' stars glam up for James Bond world premiere Fans were shaken and stirred as stars of the latest 007 film 'Spectre' brought plenty of glamour to the red carpet for the film's world premiere at London's Royal Albert Hall on Oct. 26, 2015. Photo: LEON NEAL/Getty Images./ Published: 10/26/2015 3:57:26 Lea Seydoux, Daneil Craig and Monica Bellucci French actress Lea Seydoux, British actor Daniel Craig and Italian actress Monica Bellucci pose on arrival for the world premiere of the new James Bond film "Spectre" at the Royal Albert Hall in London on Oct. 26, 2015. The film is directed by Sam Mendes and sees Daniel Craig play suave MI6 spy 007 for a fourth time. 1 of 15
